00:00:41.681 --> 00:00:46.735
Today Swathi is going to show us how to cook Onion Rings

00:00:48.731 --> 00:00:50.957
Ingredients required for Onion Rings

00:00:51.223 --> 00:01:00.312
Maida Flour, Corn Flour, Bread Crumbs, 
Baking Soda, Salt, Red Chilli Powder, Onions &amp; Oil

00:01:06.653 --> 00:01:15.014
First take a bowl and add half cup of maida flour in it

00:01:17.044 --> 00:01:25.786
Add three spoons of corn flour in it

00:01:28.032 --> 00:01:38.609
Add some salt and red chilli powder into the bowl as per taste

00:01:42.182 --> 00:01:45.297
Add a pinch of baking soda into the bowl

00:02:01.020 --> 00:02:12.120
Add five spoons of bread crumbs into the bowl

00:02:14.814 --> 00:02:22.845
Bread crumbs are easily available in market
 or else dry the thick edges of the bread 
pieces and grind them to get bread crumbs

00:02:33.037 --> 00:02:42.828
Now add some water in it and
 mix them well until it turns into a batter

00:02:52.262 --> 00:03:00.738
Heat some oil in a pan for deep fry

00:03:31.100 --> 00:03:37.324
Now cut the onions into thick slices and
 separate the onion roundles into rings

00:03:41.928 --> 00:03:57.123
Dip the sliced onion rings into the
 prepared batter and deep fry them

00:04:31.115 --> 00:04:36.083
Remove the fried onion rings into a plate

00:04:39.964 --> 00:04:45.244
Serve the onion rings with some tomato ketchup

